OBJECTIVE: To quantify the burden of disease and injury for the Aboriginal and 
non-Aboriginal populations in the Northern Territory.
DESIGN AND SETTING: Analysis of Northern Territory data for 1 January 1994 to 30 
December 1998 from multiple sources.
MAIN OUTCOME MEASURES: Disability-adjusted life-years (DALYs), by age, sex, 
